@startuml
title Green Rides System States

[*] --> Login

state Login
Login : entry / To Action
Login : do / Log in to the system
Login : exit / Username and password entered

state JourneyDetails
JourneyDetails : entry / Display journey details
JourneyDetails : do / Show route and estimated time
JourneyDetails : exit / User has viewed details

state DrivingMode
DrivingMode : entry / Activate driving mode
DrivingMode : do / Start navigation
DrivingMode : exit / User has chosen driving mode

state OtherOptions
OtherOptions : entry / Choose other options
OtherOptions : do / Show available options
OtherOptions : exit / User has chosen other options

state EatPlace
EatPlace : entry / Select place to eat
EatPlace : do / Show menu and allow order
EatPlace : exit / User has placed order

state Accident
Accident : entry / Inform authorities
Accident : do / Send notification
Accident : exit / Authorities notified

state Feedback
Feedback : entry / Provide feedback
Feedback : do / Collect user feedback
Feedback : exit / Feedback submitted

Login --> JourneyDetails : [login success]

JourneyDetails --> DrivingMode : [user chooses driving mode]
JourneyDetails --> OtherOptions : [user chooses other options]

JourneyDetails --> EatPlace : [user is hungry]

DrivingMode --> JourneyDetails : [user needs to view details again]

OtherOptions --> JourneyDetails : [user needs to view details again]

EatPlace --> JourneyDetails : [user has finished eating]

JourneyDetails --> Accident : [accident occurs]

Accident --> JourneyDetails : [user needs to view details again]

JourneyDetails --> Feedback : [journey completed]

Feedback --> [*]

@enduml
